snippet.title: IMMORTAL HUNTERS Gameplay Walkthrough FULL DEMO - No Commentary
snippet.description:
Immortal Hunters Full Demo Gameplay Walkthrough No Commentary PC

Co-op RPG beat 'em up. People killed the underground god, stole his power and built a civilization ruled by the Church which is served by powerful immortal Hunters. Choose your hero, survive the apocalypse, fight, find a reborn god, expose the lies of the Cardinals.
